### word.http

@base = http://localhost:5000/api/v1

### Extract words (public — ไม่ต้อง login)
POST {{base}}/words/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog. The fox was very quick and clever."
}

###

### Save words (ต้อง login ก่อน — cookie จะถูกส่งอัตโนมัติถ้าใช้ REST Client)
POST {{base}}/words
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "words": [
    { "word": "quick", "source": "The quick brown fox" },
    { "word": "clever", "source": "The fox was very quick and clever." }
  ]
}

###

### Get saved words
GET {{base}}/words

###

### Export words as .txt
GET {{base}}/words/export

###

### Delete a word (แทน :id ด้วย _id จริงจาก GET response)
DELETE {{base}}/words/REPLACE_WITH_WORD_ID

###
